00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:37,600
[SPEAKER_01] onda noga u šlap je, ugasi, ono.

133
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je, to je, mi smo bili opasni, tipo, iza kamere.

134
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:43,240
