[SPEAKER_01] ne treba nigdje,

984
01:12:01,760 --> 01:12:02,899
[SPEAKER_01] ali igdje treba,

985
01:12:02,899 --> 01:12:03,600
[SPEAKER_01] igdje ne treba,

986
01:12:03,600 --> 01:12:04,199
[SPEAKER_01] uvjetno rečeno.

987
01:12:04,199 --> 01:12:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja govorim,

988
01:12:04,880 --> 01:12:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš mi to,

989
01:12:05,500 --> 01:12:05,779
[SPEAKER_01] znaš,

990
01:12:05,779 --> 01:12:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] razgovaram isključivo na razini faktografije

991
01:12:08,920 --> 01:12:11,659
[SPEAKER_01] i ajmo samo ispravno vredovat sve.

992
01:12:11,659 --> 01:12:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa drugo ne tražem,

993
01:12:12,960 --> 01:12:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] nego pošteni i sudi u svemu.

994
01:12:14,659 --> 01:12:14,939
[SPEAKER_00] Da,

995
01:12:14,939 --> 01:12:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] i nije naravno razgovar.

996
01:12:16,460 --> 01:12:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] A ne,

997
01:12:16,739 --> 01:12:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] kad ona ovako,

998
01:12:17,439 --> 01:12:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] kad ja dobar si,

999
01:12:18,140 --> 01:12:19,239
[SPEAKER_01] govorim da sam dobar.

1000
01:12:19,239 --> 01:12:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja govorim,

1001
01:12:19,579 --> 01:12:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] ha dobar sam,

1002
01:12:20,180 --> 01:12:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim,

1003
01:12:20,619 --> 01:12:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] dobare,

1004
01:12:21,000 --> 01:12:22,020
[SPEAKER_01] buko mi to mi stvorio,

1005
01:12:22,020 --> 01:12:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim,

1006
01:12:22,579 --> 01:12:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ti rekao odmah.

1007
01:12:24,260 --> 01:12:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] I tako treba jednostavno,

1008
01:12:25,640 --> 01:12:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] hrabro i smijono,

1009
01:12:26,579 --> 01:12:27,359
